Class LoadedJPPlugin

java.lang.Object
com.tom.jpedit.util.LoadedJPPlugin
public class LoadedJPPlugin extends Object
This class is an internal representation of a JPEditPlugin after it has been loaded by the program This class is specific to the function of the program and should not be interacted with by a particular plugin's implementation. For information on implementing a plugin see JPEditPlugin
